sections.Biography:
===Background===
Eglantine is a [[septa]] of the [[Faith of the Seven]]. She serves at the [[Red Keep]] in [[King's Landing]] as governess and companion to Princess [[Myrcella Baratheon]].

===[[Season 2]]===
Eglantine is among the royal entourage for a tourney to celebrate King [[Joffrey Baratheon]]'s [[nameday]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The North Remembers]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

Eglantine watches over Princess Myrcella as she plays blind man's buff with two courtiers.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

[[File:Myrcella leaves.jpg|right|thumb|200px|Eglantine accompanies Myrcella on her journey.]]
Eglatine accompanies Princess Myrcella, now a ward of [[House Martell]], on her journey from [[King's Landing]] as they travel to [[Sunspear]] as part of the betrothal arranged by Princess Myrcella's uncle [[Tyrion Lannister]] of Princess Myrcella to Prince [[Trystane Martell]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Old Gods and the New]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
